==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Grandiloquence
<hw>Gran*dil"o*quence</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The use of
lofty words or phrases; bombast; -- usually in a bad sense.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The sin of <qex>grandiloquence</qex> or tall talking.</q>
<rj><qau>Thackeray,</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Grandiloquent</ent>⟦br⟧
